---
layout: base
title: Publications
description: Peer-reviewed and forthcoming publications by Mert Biricik in cybersecurity, memory forensics, BCI, and critical infrastructure protection.
priority: 0.8
changefreq: monthly
---

<section class="container-wide py-10 sm:py-14">
  <div class="masthead">
    <span class="eyebrow-blood">Folio IV</span>
    <span class="eyebrow">Register of publications</span>
  </div>

  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 mt-10">
    <div class="lg:col-span-8 lg:pr-10 lg:border-r-2 lg:border-ink-900 dark:lg:border-bone-100">
      <span class="section-marker">Acta</span>
      <h2 class="display-1 mt-5 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50 text-balance">Publications.</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 font-serif text-xl text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200 leading-relaxed">
        Peer-reviewed work and active manuscripts across cybersecurity, memory forensics, brain-computer interfaces, and AI-driven protection of critical infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em]">
        <a href="{{ metadata.social.scholar }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline hover:underline">→ Indexed at Google Scholar</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-4">
      <span class="section-marker">Tally</span>
      <dl class="mt-5">
        <div class="def-row">
          <dt class="def-key">Total entries</dt>
          <dd class="font-display text-2xl text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">{{ publications | length }}</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="def-row">
          <dt class="def-key">Published</dt>
          <dd class="font-display text-2xl text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">{% set published = 0 %}{% for p in publications %}{% if p.status == 'published' %}{% set published = published + 1 %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}{{ published }}</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="def-row">
          <dt class="def-key">In review</dt>
          <dd class="font-display text-2xl text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">{% set rev = 0 %}{% for p in publications %}{% if p.status == 'under-review' %}{% set rev = rev + 1 %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}{{ rev }}</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="def-row">
          <dt class="def-key">In preparation</dt>
          <dd class="font-display text-2xl text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">{% set prep = 0 %}{% for p in publications %}{% if p.status == 'in-preparation' or p.status == 'ready' %}{% set prep = prep + 1 %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}{{ prep }}</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container-wide section-tight">
  <ol class="border-t-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
    {% for pub in publications %}
    <article class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 py-10 border-b-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <span class="font-blackletter text-5xl text-blood-700 dark:text-blood-400 leading-none">{{ pub.year }}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 md:pr-6 md:border-r-2 md:border-ink-900 dark:md:border-bone-100">
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl leading-tight text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">
          {% if pub.link %}<a href="{{ pub.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ pub.title }}</a>{% else %}{{ pub.title }}{% endif %}
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 font-serif italic text-ink-500 dark:text-bone-300">{{ pub.authors | join(', ') }}</p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-serif text-base sm:text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200">{{ pub.summary }}</p>

        {% if pub.tags %}
        <ul class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          {% for t in pub.tags %}<li class="tag">{{ t }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-4">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow mb-2">Venue</p>
          <p class="font-display text-base text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">{{ pub.venue }}</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow mb-2">Status</p>
          {% if pub.status == 'published' %}<span class="status-published">Published</span>
          {% elif pub.status == 'under-review' %}<span class="status-review">Under review</span>
          {% elif pub.status == 'ready' %}<span class="status-ready">Ready</span>
          {% elif pub.status == 'in-preparation' %}<span class="status-prep">In preparation</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if pub.doi %}
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow mb-2">DOI</p>
          <a href="{{ pub.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] no-underline hover:underline break-all">{{ pub.doi }}</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>

<div class="container-wide section-tight">
  <div class="masthead">
    <span class="eyebrow-blood">§ Annexe</span>
    <span class="eyebrow">Domains of inquiry</span>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 border-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
    <div class="p-7 border-b-2 md:border-b-0 md:border-r-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
      <span class="font-blackletter text-3xl text-blood-700 dark:text-blood-400">I</span>
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl mt-1 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">Critical infrastructure security</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200 leading-relaxed">SCADA threat discovery, OSINT-based assessments, anomaly detection in power distribution networks.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-7 border-b-2 md:border-b-0 md:border-r-2 border-ink-900 dark:border-bone-100">
      <span class="font-blackletter text-3xl text-blood-700 dark:text-blood-400">II</span>
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl mt-1 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">Memory forensics</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200 leading-relaxed">Unsupervised triage on Volatility3 artefacts; behavioural and graph-theoretic features against fileless malware.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-7">
      <span class="font-blackletter text-3xl text-blood-700 dark:text-blood-400">III</span>
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl mt-1 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">EEG / BCI signal processing</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200 leading-relaxed">Real-time change-point detection (PELT) for asynchronous BCI on edge devices.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="fleuron"><span class="font-blackletter text-2xl">✠</span></div>

  <div class="text-center">
    <h2 class="display-3 text-ink-900 dark:text-bone-50">Joint inquiry?</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-serif italic text-lg text-ink-700 dark:text-bone-200 max-w-xl mx-auto">Particularly interested in joint work bridging applied cybersecurity, anomaly detection, and edge AI.</p>
    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-solid">→ Reach out</a>
      <a href="/projects/" class="btn-ghost">View related projects</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
